    • formatAndTranslate

      static String formatAndTranslate(String keyMessage, Object... args)
      Used to factorize code and increase readability by avoiding String.format(I18n.get(...), ..., ...) calls.
      Parameters:
      keyMessage - the key of the message in the i18n file
      args - the arguments to replace in the message
      Returns:
      the formatted and translated message
